{"tid":2307344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足球籃球最多2人一組！！！！","createTime":"2020-12-01T06:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T13:08:31.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5919cf65d026d68011d5f0341f59ecf2eb480554","tid":2307344,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"【限聚令、罰款、工展會】新冠肺炎第四波疫情未受控，衞生署昨(11月30日)公布新增76宗確診個案，累計6,315人確診，跳舞群組增至520人染疫。消息指，今日新增大概84宗確診個案，包括三名醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n港府宣布明天(2日)起收緊防疫措施，包括限聚令回復至2人，食肆晚上10時後禁堂食，並關閉卡拉OK、泳池、麻雀館等，大部分公務員在家工作。海洋公園及迪士尼樂園被勒令周三起關閉。<br />\n<br />\n政府公布收緊防疫措施，體育場所限最多2人一組運動，即足球、籃球等多人參與的運動，都難以按正常人數進行。體育場所的觀眾席亦必須關閉。除了飲食、淋浴、戶外運動時，其他時間均要戴口罩。"},{"pid":"f96b5f1e21181241db2c4e34afa3a08e76c0ff62","tid":2307344,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"炒場師又要收皮"},{"pid":"ed7b69494b869a753ee42d23dd439c866ad8f9e4","tid":2307344,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"肺炎時期仲玩玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好selfish"},{"pid":"6c006c951e8e690dce4f1519701ae65cb3cae3f8","tid":2307344,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"體育場所的觀眾席亦必須關閉<br />\n<br />\n人瑞演唱會係唔係開唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952a41eb9bb335437e199fad21e3c30baf7a3b46","tid":2307344,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"林鄭信運動救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想前線操fit d"},{"pid":"62406a9246ca93cdb3b9c9dd9ffa29f47b663db2","tid":2307344,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"跳舞撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75a0199cd